name: The Biomedical Knowledge Engineering Group (BMKEG)
tagline: Open source code generated at BMKEG@ISI
body: We are an [academically-funded, open source, biomedical informatics software development shop](http://www.isi.edu/research_groups/bmkeg). We are funded from academic sources and have a strong commitment to develop open knowledge systems to assist and support biomedical scientists in their everyday work.
